---
title: Double Sri Lankan-Spiced Salmon & Fries with Pear Salad & Garlic Aioli
description: Tonight, we're taking omega-3 rich salmon to the next level with our Sri Lankan-inspired seasoning. Add oven-baked fries and garlic aioli for a touch of creaminess, and you have a nutritionally balanced meal that's simply delicious!
